@node main

              PS2PK V1.4 & V1.5 written by Piet Tutelaers

              Amiga Port SMps2pk done by Reinhard Katzmann

                  Warning: PS2PK V1.5 is in Beta stage!


Sorry, this is not yet a real AmigaGuide. I'm currently developping a program
which simplifies Guide creating a lot (including a full GUI) and will use this
Guide (among others) as a test Guide. You can use the CLI-only version of this
program (GuideToolV1.0, avalaible on Aminet) to create an Index and to add
Cross References if you wish to. It is partly written by me and parts of it
are from the files distributed by the author.

This is more or less a preliminary release. I did not test the PS2PK V1.5
binaries very close. The only known problems to me so far are path problems
(deriving from UNIX: ./ is used as current directory on this platform).

I did not include the sources (and also not the diffs-yet) to keep the size of
the archive down. They can be found at CTAN: fonts/utilities/ps2pk/...
The doc files (*.1, Unix manual pages) did not make it in the guide yet, sorry
but this will happen in the next release, so try to be a bit patient.

I also will include Version strings (including Amiga Revision) in the next
release. Consider the current Revision of all binaries as "1".

